body: When the on-screen selector is turned on before any node in the widget tree has been selected, it's difficult to confirm its state due to lack of visual feedback.

comment_data.body: @jacob314, I think you have some code written for this?
@devoncarew @jacob314 This has moved milestones six times. Should we plan on doing it later than M31? Or is this really a bug that can be fixed for M31?
It'll require a change in package:flutter, so won't hit in the M31 timeframe. I'll conservatively bump it to the 'on deck' milestone.

milestone.description: Issues under consideration for upcoming milestones.
milestone.title: On Deck

title: Provide visual feedback when the on-screen selector is on
